node.text:
The new BUGATTI smartwatch range, created with VIITA Watches, mirrors the unrivalled precision, artistry and technology synonymous with hyper sports cars crafted in Molsheim. Each of the models offers an innumerable amount of technical features and is built by hand with meticulous attention to detail for a seamless integration of more than 1,000 individual parts. Discover the collection at www.bugatti.com or www.bugatti-smartwatches.com. @bugatti_smartwatches

#BUGATTI #BUGATTILifestyle #BUGATTISmartwatches #VIITA #VIITAforBUGATTI #VIITAWatches

Twin Turbo Furious Bugatti 300+ echoes the hypercar’s materials and colors, while introducing a brand-new aesthetic and technology. The case alone for example is comprised of 88 parts and made of forged carbon, with a titanium core to ensure water resistance. This exclusive time piece is limited to 3 units. 
#Jacobandco #CHIRONSuperSport300+

node.title: Jacob&Co. for BUGATTI: Twin Turbo Furious Bugatti 300+

node.text: No other driver spends more time in a BUGATTI CHIRON than he does: Andy Wallace. In the last few years, the Englishman and Pilote Officiel covered a total of over 150,000 km in the hyper sports cars from Molsheim. He thus is the perfect person to show owners and fans how to make the most of this unique vehicle. In a series of five video clips, Andy explains the car’s technical details in a comprehensible manner and reveals what the CHIRON is capable of and still driving it safely. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

node.title: Andy Wallace: How to ... Chiron - Episode 5: The Speed Key

He thus is the perfect person to show owners and fans how to make the most of this unique vehicle. In a series of five video clips, Andy explains the car’s technical details in a comprehensible manner and reveals what the CHIRON is capable of and still driving it safely. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

Expertly examined for absolute perfection under BUGATTI’s quality light tunnel in the Atelier at Molsheim sits the one-off LA VOITURE NOIRE. Hundreds of assembly hours culminate in the final quality audit, whereby BUGATTI’s most exclusive hyper sports car is inspected down to the final stitch by the expert eyes of BUGATTI’s craftspeople.

The reminiscence of an icon, but also a tribute to BUGATTI’s more than 110-year history, LA VOITURE NOIRE is the manifesto of the Bugatti aesthetic and a piece of automotive haute couture.

node.text:
Once final assembly is complete, all BUGATTI hyper cars undergo a rigorous and intensive final quality audit to check for even the most miniscule of imperfections. Nothing passes through unless perfection is achieved. Company founder Ettore Bugatti himself would expect nothing less.
 
In the case of the world-renowned and one-off LA VOITURE NOIRE, the time spent to complete the final audit has been double. In its duty to pay homage to one of the most prized automobiles in history, the BUGATTI Type 57 SC Atlantic, ensuring absolute flawlessness and excellence is paramount. 
 
#BUGATTI #BUGATTILaVoitureNoire #LAVOITURENOIRE

Every BUGATTI represents a truly unique automotive masterpiece and the DIVO ‘Lady Bug’, with its geometric-dynamic algorithmic pattern of 1,600 diamond shapes, took our marque’s craftsmanship expertise to a new level entirely.
 
Working in close collaboration with the DIVO customer, BUGATTI’s designers and engineers spent two years perfecting the intricate outlines, including figuring out the complex puzzle of how to paint each carbon fibre panel of the DIVO with absolute precision.
 
[photo courtesy of @rickyverdugo]

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIDivo #DIVO

The French Riviera is one of Europe's most exclusive summer destinations. Idyllic marinas with crystal-clear waters, it never fails to attract an international audience. The coastal town of Saint-Tropez is therefore an ideal place for our marque to present its latest models to our customers and prospective owners, at the BUGATTI Summer Road Show.

node.text:
The BUGATTI Divo is now a cornerstone of our marque’s history spanning more than 110 years. When true coachbuilding was revived for the 21st century, the DIVO represented more than the sum of its hand-built parts.

Visually and technically different from the CHIRON, the DIVO set a new standard with its bespoke, intricate, and complex design. With a chassis composed to conquer corners and propelled by the legendary 8.0-liter W16 engine with 1,500 PS, the 40th and final DIVO will forever be revered as an icon.
 
#BUGATTI #BUGATTIDivo #DIVO

The end of a chapter in BUGATTI‘s illustrious history. The 40th and final DIVO leaves the Atelier in Molsheim on the way to its new European owner.

Rounding off the three-year development and production period of BUGATTI’s 21st century coach-built masterpiece: when launched in 2018, the DIVO represented the beginning of a new era for the French marque. Returning to our roots of coachbuilding in the 1920s and 1930s, each DIVO has been uniquely customized by the respective owner, entirely in keeping with BUGATTI’s coachbuilding tradition.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIDivo #DIVO

BUGATTI‘s “La Maison Pur Sang” program is the ultimate seal of authenticity for all past, present and future examples of our marque‘s hyper sports cars.

Models from BUGATTI‘s illustrious history will undergo an extensive certification process at the home of BUGATTI in Mosheim, France. The program also offers customers and collectors an intensive range of restoration and reconfiguration options. 

The very first model to receive “La Maison Pur Sang” certification of authenticity is a stunning 2008 VEYRON 16.4 Grand Sport, which has been meticulously restored to its launch specification by the Molsheim team of experts over a period of four months.
